textBox.richText: Now, I don’t know about this one. It’s something entirely different but also something that I’ve been wanting to try for a while. Benv20 contacted me about doing some sort of collab, and he offered me his voice, which I so eagerly accepted. I hope the joke comes across. Also, I’m so silly, for I removed the background music instead of lowering it. And another thing, I don’t even think that the title makes sense! I mean, it might. Also, he isn’t a Voice Actor if it’s just himself. That’s silly. Benv20 is the Voice Actor, RED is the character...
